# Public, build-time config (Vite inlines VITE_* into the browser bundle).
# Do NOT put secrets here — this file is committed.
#
# The live-run backend URL is intentionally NOT hardcoded in this public repo.
# - For the maintainer's deploy: set a GitHub Actions repo VARIABLE named
#   VITE_BACKEND_URL (Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions → Variables).
# - For your own deploy: set VITE_BACKEND_URL to your backend, or leave it blank
#   and enter the backend URL in the app's ⚙ Settings at runtime.
# - For local dev: put it in code/.env.local (gitignored).
#
# VITE_BACKEND_URL=
